		<li>If we send a link to a survey on email immediately, the user could fill in survey twice unless we also update confirmation pages. We will monitor this to see how often this causes confusion</li>
		<li>Data will be anonymised (GUID)</li>
		<li>Should "contact later" version not have desired effect, we will try the alternative</li>
