<h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Hypotheses</h3>
	<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
		<li>We believe that response rate will be increased by including user satisfaction within journey</li>
		<li>We believe that users are skimming over the link to survey on the confirmation page. </li>
		<li>We believe that users are already undertaking a task in addition to normal requirements. This makes it unlikely that they will volunteer to complete an additional task immediately.</li>
		<li>We believe that requiring user to make a selection before submitting will increase take up</li>
		<li>We believe that requiring user to make a selection before submitting will not reduce reporting quantity</li>
		<li>We believe that requiring user to make a selection before submitting will not increase colleagues anxiety</li>	</ul>
